quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,41,"Naho ba bandi bimutse kubera Allah nyuma y’uko barenganyijwe, tuzabatuza aheza ku isi, ariko mu by’ukuri igihembo cyo ku munsi w’imperuka ni cyo gihebuje; iyo baza kubimenya"
  16,42,(Abo ni) ba bandi bihanganye kandi bakiringira Nyagasani wabo (wenyine)
  16,43,Kandi mbere yawe nta bandi batari abagabo twigeze twohereza ngo tubahishurire ubutumwa. Ngaho (yemwe babangikanyamana b’i Maka) nimubaze abahawe ubumenyi (bw’ibitabo byo hambere) niba mutabizi
  16,44,"(Twazohereje zizanye) ibimenyetso bigaragara n’ibitabo (bitagatifu). Twanakumanuriye (yewe Muhamadi) urwibutso (Qur’an) kugira ngo usobanurire abantu ibyo bahishuriwe, ndetse no kugira ngo batekereze (ku bikubiye muri Qur’an banayisobanukirwe)"
  16,45,"Ese ba bandi bacuze imigambi mibisha bibwira ko batekanye ku buryo Allah atabarigitisha mu butaka, cyangwa ko batagerwaho n’ibihano biturutse aho batakekaga"
  16,46,"Cyangwa akabagwa gitumo bajya cyangwa bava (mu mirimo yabo), uko byagenda kose ntibananirana (nta ho bacikira ibihano bya Allah)"
  16,47,"Cyangwa akabagwa gitumo bafite ubwoba (bwo kubura imitungo n’ubuzima byabo)? Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wanyu ni Nyiribambe, Nyirimbabazi"
  16,48,"Ese ntibabona uko ibicucucucu by’ibintu Allah yaremye bibogamira iburyo n’ibumoso byumvira Allah, ndetse binicisha bugufi (ku mategeko ye)"
  16,49,"Kandi ibiremwa byose biri mu birere, ibigenda ku isi ndetse n’abamalayika, byubamira Allah kandi ntibyishyira hejuru"
  16,50,"Bitinya Nyagasani wabyo uri hejuru yabyo, kandi bikora ibyo byategetswe"